casebody.data:
O’Connor, Respondent, v. A. C. Nellis Co., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from first district court.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Van Hoesen, J.

Wilmot & Gage, for appellant. J. F. Rogers, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
